I have **B.A. in Philosophy** (Roma Tre University), a **M.Sc. in Neuroscience** (School of Mind and Brain, Berlin), and I am finishing a **PhD in Psychology.**

I have extensive experience in:

-   all stages of research (study design, programming experiments/questionnaires, collecting data online, in the lab and in the field, analyzing data, writing research papers)

-   supervising students (Bachelor's and Master's)

-   coordinating research projects.

